304
00:20:17,470 --> 00:20:19,510
Obviously, Heaven wants us
to spend some alone time together.

305
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:21,540
You can't run away from fate.

306
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:23,100
Miss.

307
00:20:23,470 --> 00:20:25,470
I have something urgent to handle in Jingnan.

308
00:20:25,710 --> 00:20:27,710
