Don't write such fancy words for the Chief.

385
00:25:31,620 --> 00:25:32,300
She can't remember them.

386
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:33,230
(Eradicate them all!)

387
00:26:22,710 --> 00:26:23,430
Seventy-nine.

388
