00:26:54,820 --> 00:26:55,820
Young Lady, I'm coming to help you!

394
00:26:56,100 --> 00:26:56,780
Out of the way!

395
00:26:56,780 --> 00:26:57,670
Can't you see I have help already?

396
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:19,780
Even with the enemy in front of us,

397
00:27:19,780 --> 00:27:21,190
