476
00:32:10,990 --> 00:32:12,140
Your Highness.

477
00:32:12,580 --> 00:32:14,340
What I want is you,

478
00:32:14,620 --> 00:32:16,030
not an official position.

479
00:32:17,180 --> 00:32:18,660
I saved your life,

480
00:32:18,660 --> 00:32:19,950
and we spent a night together.

481
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:22,790
The Crown Prince gave me
his treasured ornament as the engagement gift,

482
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:25,100
