00:35:42,350 --> 00:35:44,140
are both unfit to become the Crown Princess.

554
00:35:44,830 --> 00:35:46,580
The Spring Hunt is on the 15th day of this month.

555
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:48,220
Get ready for it.

556
00:35:49,140 --> 00:35:49,870
Yes, Your Majesty.

557
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:10,720
[Ministry of Justice]

558
00:36:22,300 --> 00:36:22,990
(Ziyuan.)

559
00:36:24,390 --> 00:36:25,220
(The Dongqian Pirates have been exterminated,)

560
00:36:26,740 --> 00:36:28,910
(but I still couldn't earn a chance
for you to leave the mountains.)

561
00:36:30,660 --> 00:36:31,550
(In the entire Jing State,)

562
00:36:33,140 --> 00:36:35,390
(I can only share my woes with Luo Mingxi.)

563
00:36:36,950 --> 00:36:37,580
(And I)

564
00:36:38,660 --> 00:36:40,140
(can only reminisce time and again)

565
00:36:41,580 --> 00:36:43,220
(so that I can remember your eyes and draw them.)

566
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:04,030
Your Highness.

567
00:37:07,550 --> 00:37:08,660
Luo Mingxi.

568
00:37:09,260 --> 00:37:11,220
You should change your bad habit

569
00:37:11,550 --> 00:37:12,470
of walking stealthily.

570
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:15,070
This is how I have always been walking.

571
00:37:15,470 --> 00:37:16,740
Your Highness, you should get used to it.

572
00:37:18,220 --> 00:37:18,830
Have a seat.

573
00:37:24,260 --> 00:37:25,620
Why have you come to visit me

574
00:37:25,620 --> 00:37:26,390
at this late hour?

575
00:37:34,350 --> 00:37:35,870
What's the point of yearning for her?

576
00:37:36,430 --> 00:37:38,390
The emperor still refuses to release Ziyuan.

577
00:37:38,830 --> 00:37:41,070
Moreover, during the Spring Hunt
in a few days' time,

578
00:37:41,350 --> 00:37:43,990
the emperor has invited
many noble ladies for you to meet.

579
00:37:46,070 --> 00:37:46,740
That's why

580
00:37:46,740 --> 00:37:48,180
you're the only one

581
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:51,580
I can talk to about Ziyuan.

582
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:55,220
I've never felt pressured
by the palace's constant urging.

583
00:37:56,140 --> 00:37:57,620
I'm just scared that since ten years have passed,

584
00:37:58,780 --> 00:37:59,430
even I am beginning

585
00:37:59,430 --> 00:38:00,660
to forget what she looks like.

586
00:38:10,950 --> 00:38:13,510
She must have grown older, taller,

587
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:16,220
and become different from what we recall,

588
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,780
but her eyes would never change.

589
00:38:31,430 --> 00:38:32,620
It's her eyes.

590
00:38:34,740 --> 00:38:35,350
Just remembering

591
00:38:35,350 --> 00:38:37,220
how she looked at me with those eyes,

592
00:38:38,470 --> 00:38:40,780
I can never enjoy the extravagant banquets

593
00:38:41,430 --> 00:38:43,910
His Majesty has prepared for me.

594
00:38:44,430 --> 00:38:46,580
(The late emperor appointed me
as the next Crown Princess.)

595
00:38:46,950 --> 00:38:48,620
(Did he ask for my opinion back then?)

596
00:38:49,140 --> 00:38:51,140
His Majesty reserves the position
of the Crown Princess for me.

597
00:38:51,470 --> 00:38:52,990
Again, has he ever asked for my opinion?

598
00:39:17,350 --> 00:39:19,180
The Crown Prince is here.

599
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:20,140
The Crown Prince is here.

600
00:39:20,140 --> 00:39:21,030
It really is him.

601
00:39:21,260 --> 00:39:22,180
It's His Highness!

602
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:31,660
I heard that a female pirate

603
00:39:31,660 --> 00:39:33,070
is trying to marry the Crown Prince.

604
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:34,300
What a joke.

605
00:39:34,300 --> 00:39:35,180
Exactly.

606
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:37,220
His Highness is so dashing.

607
00:39:37,220 --> 00:39:39,180
He wouldn't pay attention to a pirate.

608
00:39:39,660 --> 00:39:40,550
Exactly.

609
00:39:48,140 --> 00:39:49,740
What do you think

610
00:39:49,740 --> 00:39:51,070
Ren Anle looks like?

611
00:39:51,740 --> 00:39:53,070
She must be a barbarian

612
00:39:53,070 --> 00:39:54,220
with strong, burly arms.

613
00:39:54,220 --> 00:39:54,780
Right?

614
00:39:57,740 --> 00:39:59,700
I'm going to bet that she's a beauty, though.

615
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:03,660
Wen Shuo.

616
00:40:04,300 --> 00:40:06,100
You're joining our bet too?

617
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:07,350
Someone who could fight alongside the Crown Prince

618
00:40:07,620 --> 00:40:08,660
[Page to the Crown Prince, Wen Shuo]
to defeat the Dongqian Pirates

619
00:40:08,830 --> 00:40:10,100
could never be an ugly woman.

620
00:40:11,780 --> 00:40:12,910
Everyone knows that the Crown Prince

621
00:40:12,910 --> 00:40:14,550
is pining for someone.

622
00:40:14,550 --> 00:40:16,430
Even though she can't leave Dai Mountain,

623
00:40:16,430 --> 00:40:18,100
she won't get replaced easily

624
00:40:18,100 --> 00:40:19,070
by a female pirate.

625
00:40:19,990 --> 00:40:20,780
Exactly.

626
00:40:20,950 --> 00:40:23,430
Do you think the Crown Prince
has really fallen in love with her?

627
00:40:23,430 --> 00:40:24,510
I don't think so.

628
00:40:24,910 --> 00:40:26,100
I don't think so, either.

629
00:40:29,350 --> 00:40:31,430
Now, everyone in the upper echelons of the state

630
00:40:31,430 --> 00:40:33,030
must have heard

631
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:35,430
that the Crown Prince
is the most handsome man in the state,

632
00:40:35,740 --> 00:40:37,100
and even a female pirate

633
00:40:37,100 --> 00:40:39,220
is willing to offer 30,000 navy forces
just so you'll marry her.

634
00:40:39,620 --> 00:40:40,260
No.

635
00:40:41,780 --> 00:40:42,910
She wants to marry you.

636
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:45,140
Have you revised your studies?

637
00:40:49,350 --> 00:40:50,350
I know.

638
00:40:50,350 --> 00:40:52,260
Even if you do fall in love with someone else,

639
00:40:52,430 --> 00:40:54,910
only that lady in the Dai Mountain
will be the Crown Princess.

640
00:40:55,740 --> 00:40:58,350
But, we're placing bets

641
00:40:58,350 --> 00:41:00,700
on whether Ren Anle is pretty or burly.

642
00:41:00,700 --> 00:41:02,470
Your Highness, mind giving me a tip?

643
00:41:07,950 --> 00:41:08,620
Jili?

644
00:41:09,830 --> 00:41:10,510
Well?

645
00:41:29,950 --> 00:41:30,550
Look.

646
00:41:39,770 --> 00:41:43,470
[Ren Anle's servant, Yuanqin]

647
00:41:43,780 --> 00:41:44,580
She's

648
00:41:45,580 --> 00:41:47,740
as beautiful as the morning sun

649
00:41:48,550 --> 00:41:50,990
and a lily blossoming on a lake.

650
00:41:52,550 --> 00:41:54,180
Where did she come from?

651
00:42:35,350 --> 00:42:36,180
She killed two birds with one shot!

652
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:37,140
Amazing!

653
00:42:37,140 --> 00:42:37,830
Marvelous!

654
00:42:59,350 --> 00:43:00,220
Your Highness.

655
00:43:00,220 --> 00:43:01,180
We meet again.

656
00:43:05,350 --> 00:43:06,070
Miss?

657
00:43:06,470 --> 00:43:07,620
You are...?

658
00:43:07,620 --> 00:43:08,660
My name is Ren Anle.

659
00:43:09,180 --> 00:43:10,510
I'm here to become the Crown Princess.

660
00:43:33,740 --> 00:43:37,140
♪If I bet my all on it desperately♪

661
00:43:37,140 --> 00:43:41,100
♪I know my heart will be uneasy♪

662
00:43:41,660 --> 00:43:48,420
♪I give up on my light and hide it under a bushel♪

663
00:43:49,220 --> 00:43:52,620
♪You're the moon in my heart♪

664
00:43:52,780 --> 00:43:56,780
♪I can't dream to own you♪

665
00:43:57,180 --> 00:44:04,540
